Package: linkbreedeR
Title: Integrated Tools for Genetic Analysis and Breeding
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Author", "Name", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    linkbreedeR provides R wrappers for popular genetic analysis tools including 
    blupf90+, PLINK, and renumf90. Users can run these tools directly from R without 
    needing to separately install external software. The package includes pre-compiled 
    binaries for Linux, macOS, and Windows platforms.
